{
  "texts": [
    "The results show that Longformer outperform other baseline models.",
    "In contrast, GPT-4 exhibits the lowest ROUGE scores when compared to human-written abstracts, yet achieves high performance in both human evaluations and LLM evaluations.",
    "A case study reveals that GPT-4 frequently employs connectives, pronouns, and excessive elaboration, contributing to its lower ROUGE scores.",
    "However, its strong performance in human and LLM assessments highlights GPT-4's strengths in coherence and readability.",
    "These findings highlight the bias and limitations of using traditional summary evaluation metrics, such as ROUGE and BLEU, in assess generative models like GPT-4."
  ]
}